<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.95203.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Anthidiellum smithii (Ritsema, 1874) A, B lateral habitus of females from Myanmar (BSRU-AA- 6909) and Khon Kaen (BSRU-AA- 4482), Thailand, respectively C-F faces of Myanmar female, Khon Kaen female, and Chumporn males (BSRU-AA- 1245, 1247). Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B); 0.5 mm (C-F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/954855" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

